    {
      "id": "demo-sql-paid-orders",
      "order": 2,
      "type": "sql",
      "category": "code",
      "title": "MySQL SQL 示例：多表统计已支付订单数",
      "difficulty": "中等题",
      "difficulty_level": "medium",
      "difficulty_label": "中等题",
      "difficulty_score": 2,
      "difficulty_reason": "需要理解 users 与 orders 的 join key，并组合 JOIN、WHERE、GROUP BY、COUNT 和 ORDER BY。",
      "expected_failure_mode": "忘记 JOIN users，忘记过滤 paid 状态，或没有按 user_id 排序。",
      "problem_statement": "查询逻辑表 `users` 与 `orders`，统计每个有已支付订单的用户的已支付订单数量，并返回用户名称。\n\n你需要使用 `orders.user_id = users.id` 关联两张表，只统计 `orders.status = 'paid'` 的订单。\n\n注意：这是 MySQL-only runtime 示例。若本机未配置 `LEARN_MYSQL_*` 环境变量或未物化示例表，点击运行会显示 MySQL 配置错误；这用于检查 SQL 编辑器和错误反馈路径。",
      "input_spec": "`users(id, name, segment)` 与 `orders(order_id, user_id, status, amount)`；`orders.user_id` 关联 `users.id`。",
      "output_spec": "返回三列：`user_id`、`user_name`、`paid_order_count`，按 `user_id` 升序。",
      "constraints": [
        "只能写一条 MySQL SELECT 或 WITH 查询",
        "不能修改数据",
        "只统计 status = 'paid' 的订单"
      ],
      "starter_sql": "SELECT u.id AS user_id, u.name AS user_name, COUNT(*) AS paid_order_count\nFROM users AS u\nJOIN orders AS o ON o.user_id = u.id\nWHERE o.status = 'paid'\nGROUP BY u.id, u.name\nORDER BY u.id;\n",
      "supported_runtimes": [
        "mysql"
      ],
      "default_runtime": "mysql",
      "dataset_refs": [
        "users-public",
        "orders-public"
      ],
      "parameter_spec_ref": "demo-sql-paid-orders",
      "result_contract": {
        "columns": [
          "user_id",
          "user_name",
          "paid_order_count"
        ],
        "order_sensitive": true
      },
